                  <summary>An unillustrated copy of the <title>Silsilat al-Ẕahab</title> (Golden
                     Chain), which comprises the first of seven books in the <title>Haft
                        Awrang</title> (Seven Thrones) by the late Timurid-era poet <persName
                        key="person_90042997" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/90042997/"
                        xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">‘Abd al-Raḥmān Jāmī (d. 1492)</persName>.</summary>

